1. == handle situations where user has closed access to his/her favourites ==

	WHEN: retrieve_user_favourites returns None
	
	DISCUSSION
		how to distinguish between following situations:
					a) user's favourites were not yet parse (NULL value)
					b) user has empty favourites ('[]' value)
					c) user has blocked access to his favourites (NULL value)

